s killed him. Avenge your death brother. pic.twitter.com/LIkIKEudin — Senator Dino Melaye. (SDM) (@dino_melaye) November 17, 2019  Vanguard Nigeria News Senator Dino Melaye has come out to announce the death of his nephew, Olorunjuwon after sustaining gunshot wounds at his polling unit on Saturday. Dino Melaye announced this on his Twitter page Sunday morning saying: "My nephew Olorunjuwon who was shot at my pooling unit yesterday died this morning. My… November 17, 2019 In "Kogi" Policemen deployed at Polling Unit 006, Asuta Ward, Kabba/Bunu Local Government areas of Kogi fled after suspected thugs took over the unit. ALSO READ: KogiDecides: Dino Melaye's nephew allegedly shot at PU yesterday, dies Sunday morning At least five of the officers escaped through a nearby bush shortly after irate… November 17, 2019 In "Kogi" Senator Dino Melaye has been in the news for sometime now from certificate scandal to a video mocking his accuser with the latest being an attempt on his life. April 15, 2017 In "News"